                p This course will take you from nothing to an understanding of digital logic. We'll teach you about different electronic components and you'll <strong>build circuits</strong> that fit them together.
                p Do you know what an operation amplifier is? No? Great! You will after <strong>twelve two-hour courses taught once a week</strong>. Resistors! Diodes! Filters! Logic gates! Datasheets! We'll give you the foundation to tackle some cool projects and to continue on to bigger and better things.
